ine any purchase and we will refund your money in full. We will strive to work everything out, but we also strive to avoid any intentional or unintentional conflict in a transaction. In short, if we suspect anything, we will cancel the transaction and refund your money.</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\"><u><span style=\\"font-size: larger;\\"><strong>After Purchase Help:</strong></span></u></p>\r\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\">We strive to continue our relationship even after your purchase.</p>\r\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\">Should you have any questions after purchasing an item, we are here to help.</p>\r\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\">We also offer a full jewelers, goldsmith and watch repair services even after the items warranty expires.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');
